{"tid":2035450,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【特別服務】設計狗幫你請假","createTime":"2020-05-26T02:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:47:48.000Z","uid":116953,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc551b3dfa85b33c4804aeaed1fe80557cc702c","tid":2035450,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGranae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGranae.jpg&h=bb1a1c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【致僱主的公開信】<br />\n鑑於連日政治事件，由立法會內會的主席選舉事件，國歌法以至人大繞過立法會立法程序，授權人大常委將港區國安法納入基本法附件三等，引發一連串社會動盪，更可預視明天（5月27日）各區將會有市民因應不同意見而發生大型不安定的社會活動。<br />\n<br />\n香港設計職人工會在此發出公開信，要求各僱主務必關注員工上班情況，以其安全為首要考慮，因應明天（5月27日）不穩定的社會因素，批准員工請假或在家工作一天。<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集公司電郵地址，去信並敦促各僱主，倘僱員要求，允許員工明日休假一天或在家上班以減低風險。同時歡迎各設計師同業填妥以下表格，我們會為你發出公開信。<br />\n<br />\n去信表格：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/oU1pChuzMP95gaco9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FoU1pChuzMP95gaco9&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=c5699a13\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/oU1pChuzMP95gaco9</a><br />\n<br />\n加入香港設計職人工會，HKDIU，就係幫你DEAL！<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkdiu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkdiu&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=5f0a2d92\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkdiu</a>"},{"pid":"612845d908886ce44f89468051b6026d06d4fe3e","tid":2035450,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:25:11.000Z","msg":"5月27日要人返工即係推D員工去死！"},{"pid":"3fd5313cea031662e79b17554e9f0327fa87e768","tid":2035450,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:25:24.000Z","msg":"5月27日要人返工即係推D員工去死！"},{"pid":"6192fe28d557272fc9d30a10913f6a2213b6eb80","tid":2035450,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"5月27日要人返工即係推D員工去死！"},{"pid":"5a0b0e140723920c4e1d2a437db2b7d6d0d86a99","tid":2